<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.4">
<l>nāmam palavu muṭainā raṇanampī</l>
<l>tāmat tuḷavam mikanā ṟiṭukiṉṟīr</l>
<l>kāma ṉeṉappā ṭivantil lampukuntīr</l>
<l>ēmat tituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord Nāraṇa with many names,</l>
<l>You who dispenses the intense scent of the tulasī of [your] garland,</l>
<l>You entered [our] yard, arriving singing like the god of love</l>
<l>In the night! What is this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
